cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is about Natural Language Processing (NLP) and specifically focuses on Named Entity Recognition (NER). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of language models and word vectors, which are related to machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.LG and cs.AI likely categories as well. The paper also mentions similarity measures, which are related to information retrieval (IR), making cs.IR a possible category. Finally, since the paper focuses on NER, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a possible category.
